high_descs: Head to the white table in the living room on the left.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Head right to enter the bedroom to reach the bed.
Cut the bread on the bed with the knife.
Turn left to face the nightstand.
Put the knife in the nightstand.
Turn right to face the bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the bed.
Head to the fridge in the kitchen on the right.
Cool the slice of bread in the fridge and pull it out.
Head to the white table on the left.
Put the slice of bread on the right edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of cooled bread on the table.

high_descs: Exit the room, turn left to walk to the white table next to the couch.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around, walk straight and head right to walk down the passage and take a right turn to enter the bedroom and face the bed.
Slice the bread on the bed with the knife.
Turn left to face the nightstand.
Put the knife on the nightstand.
Turn right to face the bed
Pick up a slice of bread from the bed.
Head out of the bedroom and walk left to reach the kitchen on the right and walk up to the fridge.
Cool the slice of bread in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left and head to the white dining table.
Put the slice of the bread on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled slice of bread on the dining table.

high_descs: Walk up to leave the room, then walk across the hall towards a space between a lamp, an armchair and a round table in the top left.
Pick up a cutter from the round table.
Head back towards where you came from but continue straight, enter a first room on the right, a bedroom, and walk to the left side of the bed.
Cut a bread on the bed with the cutter.
Move to a night stand next to you.
Place the cutter on the night stand.
Move back to the bread.
Take a bread slice from the bed.
Leave the bedroom, go left and walk around a sink table to your right and then to an oven to your left.
Heat up the bread slice in the oven and then take it out.
Turn left and head to a table in front of you.
Place the bread slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated-up bread slice on the table.

high_descs: Head to the passage and turn left to reach the round coffeetable in front of the couch.
Pick up the butterknife from the table.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn right to head down the passage and reach the bread on the right and face the bed.
Cut the bread on the bed with the knife.
Turn left to reach the shelf.
Put the butterknife on the shelf.
Turn right to reach the bed.
Pick up a slice of bread from the bed.
Turn right to exit the bedroom on the left and turn left to reach the kitchen to face the fridge.
Cool the slice of bread in the fridge and take the bread out.
Turn left to reach the dining table.
Put the slice of bread on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled slice of Bread on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn left at the door, then turn left into the loving room, and go across to the coffeetable in front of the sofa.
Pick up the butterknife on the table.
Head toward the lamp and go across to the kitchen sink, go across to the first room on the right side, go across to the bread on the left corner of the bed.
Slice the bread on the bed.
Turn around to the shelf.
Place the butterknife on the shelf.
Turn to the loaf of bread on the bed.
Pick up the third slice of bread from the left.
Turn left at the door and go into the kitchen to the fridge.
Place the bread in the fridge in front of the glass, then pick the bread back up.
Turn left to the diningtable beside the fridge.
Place the bread on the back of the diningtable to the right of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of Bread on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Head out of this room through the door ahead, turning left and going until reaching the wall, then turning left to the circular white coffeetable.
Pick up the butterknife from the table.
Go back to the hallway you came from and take the first doorway on the right, approaching the side of the bread.
Slice the bread on the bed.
Turn left to the shelf.
Place the butterknife down on the shelf.
Turn back to the bed.
Pick up one slice of bread.
Exit this room the way you came in, turn left and go straight, then go towards the kitchen area on the right, heading for the fridge ahead.
Put the bread in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Go to the large dining table to the left of the fridge.
Place the bread down on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled slice of Bread on a DiningTable.
